snippet: Jim Furyk made seven birdies over his last 10 holes for a nine-under-par 63, which gave him the lead going into the final round of the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am in California.
abstract: Jim Furyk takes lead in final round of Pebble Beach National Pro-Am in California; other golf scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Jim Furyk made seven birdies over his last 10 holes for a nine-under-par 63, which gave him the lead going into the final round of the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am in California.

headline.main: Jim Furyk Grabs a Slim Lead
